node.text:
I was interviewed by @graphixly as their featured artist of the week 🤩
And we are hosting a Giveaway for you to win one of three licenses for Clip Studio Paint Pro 🥳
To join the giveaway please:
💖Follow @laovaan 
💖Follow @graphixly 
💖Comment on this post with a topic for a tutorial you would like me to cover in a future video
(Currently working on a video for painting hair but not sure yet what topic to do after 👀)

Giveaways ends on September 20th! good luck and thank you 😊

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Laovaan on September 01, 2021. May be a drawing of 1 person.

node.text:
Not sure wether I'll do it with watercolor or gouache 🤔 probably start with watercolor and if I mess up, I'll cover it 😁

#sketch #drawing #mangaart #mangadrawing #animeart #animeboy #lineart

(Edit: it sold out so quickly thank you so much, reprints will happen in probably a month hopefully🤞)
Etsy shop is open again, and finally I can present you my tiny nsfw artbook "Good Night" 🙈 it has 44 pages and artworks and the work inside is uncensored so I unfortunately can't flip through 😅
after a bit of a struggle with the printing company I don't have as many left though x") there will be a reprint, but that might take a while to restock them once they are gone, just to let you know :)
Also I added some new prints to my shop :D 
Link is in Bio but also in my story x)

node.text:
Patreon comission done 😙 
...I just noticed how much he is #manspreading 😂
I struggled a bit with the anatomy, because 9s sometimes looks small, but then there are official artworks where he looks like 1,80m at least... idk, I haven't played nier automata yet 😅

#nierautomata #digitalart

node.text:
I wanted to draw something with 2000s emo aesthetic and somehow ended up with.... cyberpunk zombie angel eating pixels :D 
At least the "broken wings" trope survived the process 😂
Anyway, I hope you like it 👉👈
Oh and I hope I can reopen my etsy shop soon. I have had some struggles with the printing company but hopefully that will resolve itself the next days 😭🤞
#digitalart
#drawing #painting #clipstudio #wacom #mobilestudiopro #mangaart #animeboy #animeart
